body_html:
Can you please fill in the issue template. It will help with solving your issue. Most importantly, which version of Tensorflow are you running as I believe that the tf.python group was deprecated in 1.0. Please post a code snippet too so we can understand what you were trying to achieve and what function you were trying to find as the error from your title suggests that you're calling something similar to tf.python.ops.array_ops.pack instead of .pack() perhaps?

EDIT: Part of me also thinks that pack became stack but I may be mistaken.
